Paper: hep-th/9202045

Date: 1992-02-13

Title: An Alternative Scenario for Non-Abelian Quantum Hair

Authors: Amitabha Lahiri

Comments: 11pp

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B297 (1992) 248-252

Topologically charged black holes in a theory with a 2-form coupled to anon-abelian gauge field are investigated. It is found that the classificationof the ground states is similar to that in the theory of non-abelian discretequantum hair.